[B]In the high end game keeping wisdom down to 200 becomes increasing difficult except possibly for gnomes. You still have options though and so do I - but its narrowing down.

My wis giving gear is down to:

7 PMM 
5 EM Helm
15 Akkirus BP 
8 Donals Legs 
5 Weight of the Gods
25 Epic
5 Medicine Totem
2 Bracer of Swirling Smoke
5 Girdle of the Dilligent
10 Lodizal Shell Shield

With a base of 118 this leaves me with 205 wis - and I can only imagine the problems a HiE with 130 base wis must have. I obviously really need to swap the PMM out for an Enshrouded Veil and there are also a few other options to lower wis - but for many other slots any upgrade would yield even more wis (SBS -> Orb of infinite Void, Donals -> Templar/Akkirus, Med Totem -> Fetish etc)

Anyway, we can see my full equipment listing at [URL=http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=9406]http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=9406[/URL]  if thats of any help.

Mikar
59th Templar of Brell
The Companions
The Tribunal[/B][/QUOTE]

